data.description: *******Viewings and visits to the property are strictly by appointment only/please don't drive down the private driveway******  Nestled in the prestigious heart of Potomac, this stunning estate exudes luxury and comfort. Spanning over 8,000 square feet, this home is an architectural masterpiece, combining state-of-the-art amenities with timeless elegance, where the owner spared no expense, investing over $1,000,000 in renovations and upgrades. As you enter through the grand foyer, you are greeted by soaring ceilings, an exquisite crystal chandelier, and an abundance of natural light. The main level boasts a formal living room, an elegant dining room perfect for hosting lavish dinners, and a spacious family room with a cozy fireplace. The recently renovated gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, marble countertops, and a large center island. A charming breakfast nook overlooks the beautifully landscaped backyard, ideal for enjoying morning coffee. Upstairs, the luxurious master suite is a private sanctuary, complete with a sitting area, two walk-in closets, and a spa-like bathroom. Five additional bedrooms, each with unique character and style, offer plenty of space for family and guests. The private outdoor space is equally impressive, with a spacious patio, manicured gardens, and a pool. Located in one of the most coveted neighborhoods in Potomac, Maryland, this home is close to top-rated schools, fine dining, and boutique shopping. With easy access to downtown Washington D.C., it's the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience.
